apart because of you.

49:59.723 --> 50:03.065
She thinks it's her hair,
her body, her voice.

50:03.100 --> 50:05.166
She worries about failing you,
but it's your failure.

50:05.201 --> 50:07.069
Get out! Just...

50:07.104 --> 50:09.434
Daddy, I know
how busy you are.

50:09.469 --> 50:11.634
You have so much
going on all the time.

50:11.669 --> 50:13.570
Running a church,
the speakin' engagements,

50:13.605 --> 50:16.441
managing Carolyn.

50:16.476 --> 50:18.641
I know about your contract
at Horizon Records.

50:18.676 --> 50:20.478
I was gonna tell you.

50:20.513 --> 50:22.249
When?
When the damn album came out?

50:22.284 --> 50:24.218
Nobody can tell you anything,
Ree. You're so jealous.

50:24.253 --> 50:25.714
Jealous? Of you two?

50:25.749 --> 50:27.188
You think you better than us?

50:27.223 --> 50:28.486
That's exactly

50:28.521 --> 50:29.454
-what she's saying.
- No!

50:29.489 --> 50:31.555
Quiet! Quiet! Quiet!

50:32.756 --> 50:35.361
You are not
leaving this family

50:35.396 --> 50:37.297
for that piece of trash.

50:39.103 --> 50:41.301
I need a change.

50:42.403 --> 50:44.601
I wanna sing what I wanna sing

50:44.636 --> 50:47.505
and I wanna dress
like I want to dress.

50:48.277 --> 50:49.606
And I want Ted to manage me.

50:51.313 --> 50:54.149
He's not worth the shit
at the bottom of my shoe.

50:54.184 --> 50:56.349
