51:12.136 --> 51:15.599
You are going to beg me
to take you back.

51:18.835 --> 51:20.637
But I won't.

51:21.310 --> 51:22.639
I won't.

51:42.826 --> 51:45.662
I'm gonna say goodbye
to my children.

51:45.697 --> 51:47.829
-Okay.
-And then we'll go.

51:47.864 --> 51:48.830
Okay.

52:03.583 --> 52:04.846
Y'all not gonna fix me a plate?

52:30.280 --> 52:32.577
with that gun in your hand?

52:36.220 --> 52:37.912
You keep beating up
these club owners,

52:37.947 --> 52:40.288
there won't be any clubs
left for me to sing at.

52:41.357 --> 52:43.621
No one disrespects us.

52:43.656 --> 52:45.524
I just don't know
what else to do...

52:46.362 --> 52:48.560
after nine albums.

52:51.367 --> 52:52.729
Yes, this is Ted White.

52:52.764 --> 52:55.402
I'm calling to speak
to Mr. Whitfield.

52:55.437 --> 52:57.734
