54:04.572 --> 54:06.407
I Never Loved A Man.

54:06.442 --> 54:08.475
Terrific. I've got the perfect
place to record it.

54:08.510 --> 54:09.839
I'm working with
this little studio

54:09.874 --> 54:11.544
down in Alabama and...

54:11.579 --> 54:13.447
Aretha's only recorded
in New York.

54:13.482 --> 54:15.548
Yeah, I know that, but I think
that's part of the problem.

54:15.583 --> 54:17.385
It's overproduced,
it's a little too polished.

54:17.420 --> 54:18.386
I mean, these boys
down there...

54:18.421 --> 54:20.014
"Boys"?

54:20.049 --> 54:21.686
Don't be offended, all right?

54:21.721 --> 54:23.985
I say boys because
they're young like Aretha,

54:24.020 --> 54:26.625
like Miss Franklin,
not because they're Negroes.

54:26.660 --> 54:28.022
These guys are
the best musicians

54:28.057 --> 54:29.727
I have ever
worked with in my life,

54:29.762 --> 54:31.564
and that's saying something.

54:31.599 --> 54:32.862
I've been doing this
a long time.

54:32.897 --> 54:34.567
They don't need
to read charts.

54:34.602 --> 54:36.899
They just feel their way
through the music.

54:36.934 --> 54:38.967
It's really something.
How does that sound to you?

54:40.410 --> 54:41.772
Sounds good.

54:41.807 --> 54:44.874
And I'm not controlling
like Hammond, okay?

54:44.909 --> 54:46.480
I'm gonna give you
plenty of space

54:46.515 --> 54:47.877
to do your thing, all right?

54:47.912 --> 54:50.319
This is your show,
Miss Franklin.

54:50.354 --> 54:51.518
Your record.

54:51.553 --> 54:52.717
Okay?

55:36.862 --> 55:38.499
This is it?

55:38.534 --> 55:41.403
What did all the glamor
at Columbia get me?

55:41.438 --> 55:42.932
Do you know who
you're messing with?

55:42.967 --> 55:44.604
"Do I know who I'm..."
Do you know who you're messing

55:44.639 --> 55:45.770
-with, buddy?
-You tryin' to screw me over,

55:45.805 --> 55:46.969
-Rick?
-You in my town now, buddy!

55:47.004 --> 55:47.640
This is my place!

55:47.675 --> 55:48.839
It's my record!

55:48.874 --> 55:50.676
Everything you see here
is mine!

55:50.711 --> 55:52.007
This is my record!

55:56.849 --> 55:58.849
Miss Franklin, Ted,

55:58.884 --> 56:00.917
