Percy Sledge had
that same look on his face

56:31.015 --> 56:32.146
when he first come in here.

56:32.984 --> 56:34.720
And then he heard 'em play

56:34.755 --> 56:38.020
and he was very satisfied
with his record.

56:38.055 --> 56:39.857
I think you will be, too.

56:39.892 --> 56:41.430
-Drink?
-We don't have time

56:41.465 --> 56:42.794
for this right now.

56:46.998 --> 56:48.404
Where can I get
a jacket like that?

56:49.000 --> 56:50.571
You'd have to come to Harlem.

56:51.871 --> 56:53.134
Always wanted to go to Harlem.

56:53.169 --> 56:54.641
Yeah.

