keep it boring?

57:18.997 --> 57:20.634
I don't know, Roger. You know
any good drummers around here?

57:20.669 --> 57:22.603
Don't, actually.

57:22.638 --> 57:24.231
It's just slow.

57:24.266 --> 57:25.870
-It's just a little slow.
