57:25.905 --> 57:27.641
All right! Come on, guys!

57:27.676 --> 57:29.643
Hang with me on this.
This is a good song!

57:29.678 --> 57:31.007
It's a great song.

57:31.042 --> 57:32.811
It is what it is.

57:41.921 --> 57:43.921
All right. Let's see
what we can make of it.

