Follow me.

59:25.354 --> 59:28.124
if I could

59:29.633 --> 59:31.226
Stop. Stop.

59:33.098 --> 59:35.197
It's too busy.

59:35.232 --> 59:36.770
Let the song do the work.

59:36.805 --> 59:37.936
Yeah, stop showing off, guys.

59:37.971 --> 59:39.135
Yeah, boys, if you're trying

59:39.170 --> 59:41.038
to impress me,
it's not working.

59:41.073 --> 59:42.875
Yeah, and more importantly,
it's startin' to piss me off.

59:42.910 --> 59:43.942
Maybe we should do
something closer

59:43.977 --> 59:45.075
to the original arrangement.

59:45.110 --> 59:46.879
Nah.
-No, it's done.

59:49.114 --> 59:50.311
You kept
steppin' on me.

59:50.346 --> 59:51.785
You were
all over the neck.

59:51.820 --> 59:52.753
I couldn't tell
what you were doing.

59:52.788 --> 59:53.886
I'm all over the neck?

59:53.921 --> 59:54.953
Find your lane, Jimmy.

59:54.988 --> 59:56.218
Look who's talkin'.

59:56.253 --> 59:57.857
They could hear
your crash in Texas.

59:57.892 --> 59:59.386
Well, my horn
arrangement's killer.

59:59.421 --> 01:00:00.959
Y'all let me know
when you're ready to hear it.

01:00:00.994 --> 01:00:01.793
You gonna
save the song, Jack?

01:00:01.828 --> 01:00:03.126
As I have on many
an occasion, okay.

01:00:03.161 --> 01:00:03.797
Okay.

01:00:04.900 --> 01:00:06.294
Good job, Jack.
- How about that.

01:00:20.244 --> 01:00:22.651
Spooner's got it!
Spooner's got it!

01:00:22.686 --> 01:00:23.784
